00042 void CDFProbeGroupInformation::SetDataSet(DataSet* ds)
00043 {
00044         if (dataSet)
00045         {
00046                 dataSet->Close();
00047                 dataSet->Delete();
00048         }
00049 
00050         dataSet = ds;
00051         dataSet->Open();
00052 
00053         const DataSetHeader& dsh = ds->Header();
00054 
00055         type = Expression;
00056         direction = 0;
00057         listCnt = 0;
00058         cellCnt = 0;
00059         probeSetNumber = 0;
00060         cellsPerList = 0;
00061 
00062         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00063 
00064         // UnitType
00065         if (dsh.FindNameValParam(CDF_UNIT_TYPE, nvt))
00066                 type = (CDFDataTypeIds)nvt.GetValueUInt8();
00067         
00068         // Direction
00069         if (dsh.FindNameValParam(CDF_DIRECTION, nvt))
00070                 direction = nvt.GetValueUInt8();
00071 
00072         // ProbeSetNumber
00073         if (dsh.FindNameValParam(CDF_PROBE_SET_NUMBER, nvt))
00074                 probeSetNumber = nvt.GetValueUInt32();
00075 
00076         // CellsPerList (cells per atom)
00077         if (dsh.FindNameValParam(CDF_CELLS_PER_ATOM, nvt))
00078                 cellsPerList = nvt.GetValueUInt8();
00079 
00080         // List (atom)
00081         if (dsh.FindNameValParam(CDF_ATOMS, nvt))
00082                 listCnt = nvt.GetValueUInt32();
00083 
00084         // Cells
00085         if (dsh.FindNameValParam(CDF_CELLS, nvt))
00086                 cellCnt = nvt.GetValueUInt32();
00087 }
